snippet.title: Trine Series 1-3 Nintendo Switch Physical Edition Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming Spring 2019! Pre-orders now available exclusively at GameStop Stores and online:
https://www.gamestop.com/nintendo-switch/games/trine-series-1-3/173287

Get ready to explore the magical world of Trine - The Trine Series 1-3 game card includes:

Trine Enchanted Edition: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/trine-enchanted-edition-switch
Trine 2: Complete Story:  https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/trine-2-complete-story-switch
Trine 3: The Artifacts of Power:  Coming Soon!

Developed by Frozenbyte and published by GameTrust.
